not.description:
If true, match the complement of simple or sequence segment.
For example, to match all visits not from "New York", we can define the
segment as follows:

      "sessionSegment": {
        "segmentFilters": [{
          "simpleSegment" :{
            "orFiltersForSegment": [{
              "segmentFilterClauses":[{
                "dimensionFilter": {
                  "dimensionName": "ga:city",
                  "expressions": ["New York"]
                }
              }]
            }]
          },
          "not": "True"
        }]
      },
